#: resources/views/modules/fan-chart/config.phtml:119
msgid ""
"Show full dates (birth, marriage, death) for early generations. Later "
"generations show year only. Marriage dates are hidden from generation 9. "
"Descendants with narrow arcs automatically use a compact year-only format."
msgstr ""
"Toon volledige datums (geboorte, huwelik, sterfte) vir vroeë generasies. "
"Latere generasies toon slegs die jaar. Huweliksdatums word vanaf generasie 9 "
"verberg. Afstammelinge met smal boogies gebruik outomaties 'n kompakte slegs-"
"jaar-formaat."

#: src/Configuration.php:214
#, php-format
